headline: Wynn Resorts Announces First Quarter Earnings Release Date
summary: LAS VEGAS, April 18, 2025--Wynn Resorts, Limited (NASDAQ: WYNN) announced today that it will release the Company’s financial results for the first quarter ended March 31, 2025 after the market close on Tuesday, May 6, 2025, followed by a conference call at 1:30 p.m. PT (4:30 p.m. ET).

headline: Houston Rockets Owner Buys Large Block of Wynn Stock
summary: Tilman Fertitta, owner of the NBA team Houston Rockets, bought the stock dip in casino and lodging firm Wynn Resorts.
